items.standfirst: Years of fighting have created a crisis among Ukrainian children, with thousands estimated to have been transferred to Russia, where some are placed in so-called "re-education camps".
items.content: Years of fighting have created a crisis among Ukrainian children, with thousands estimated to have been transferred to Russia, where some are placed in so-called "re-education camps".

ai_summary: Years of fighting have created a crisis among Ukrainian children.
Thousands of children are estimated to have been transferred to Russia.
Some children are placed in so-called "re-education camps".
The girl's parents took her to Russia.
The girl claims she was brainwashed.
